$ Javascript line writer

Line writer is a small helper that line-breaks a series of spans automatically when the end of the line is reached.

→ http://renenyffenegger.ch/notes/development/languages/JavaScript/helpers/js-line-writer/test.html[An example is here]
(Source coude on : → https://github.com/ReneNyffenegger/js-line-writer/blob/master/test.html[github])

